27:54.841 --> 27:56.809
I've already used up all my...

27:58.577 --> 28:00.579
I'm going out.

28:02.614 --> 28:04.751
-ISAAC: You're such a joy. Yeah.
-JOAN: No. Don't tell me that.

28:09.388 --> 28:11.690
Oh, my God...

28:15.294 --> 28:16.863
Hey.

28:18.464 --> 28:20.399
I'm going out.

